{"tid":1316540,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"總共33人比警察拉左","createTime":"2019-07-14T16:13:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T16:22:13.000Z","uid":89543,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fe0face270c124b69ec1351933e702af1a5b780b","tid":1316540,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:13:26.000Z","msg":"沙田區今日舉行反送中遊行，晚上有大批示威者留守，警方晚上八時許開始清場。在鄰近沙田大會堂位置，警方以涉嫌非法集結的罪名拘捕了33人，各人被帶上車。<br />\n<br />\n在晚上10時許，警方在沙田大會堂附近截查多人，並拘捕當中16男17女。他們手部放在背後並被索上索帶。被捕人士被帶上大型旅遊巴，暫時未知被帶去哪一間警署。<br />\n<br />\nsource：立場新聞"},{"pid":"1740028f5bc696faea1d8fdefa3b0e8292d5d14f","tid":1316540,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:15:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de35f61553c6e34452e4fb0405958a6e73777307","tid":1316540,"uid":267219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:15:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92401efdc3723c807d0056272c1ad34f7edc0b02","tid":1316540,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:16:33.000Z","msg":"未計新城市<br />\n十字路口果班<br />\n眾志都搭左兩個"},{"pid":"9ba805c6cf180b1a83bc65c5d09e54b9e91c9b86","tid":1316540,"uid":7818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:16:33.000Z","msg":"淨係大會堂咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c81ade619be24536826b60e451e743ab21eb7a43","tid":1316540,"uid":263883,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:17:12.000Z","msg":"明明不反對通知書去到11點 非乜撚野法集結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63a5546ff0ab74837f60c9ae7ebf6018a05489d9","tid":1316540,"uid":271199,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:17:43.000Z","msg":"應該有一百人"},{"pid":"cb981e4d7500f5921da81a6a6a53a1ba00eef29f","tid":1316540,"uid":91259,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"cite